    public class AcscGenImpl
extends AclfGenImpl
implements AcscGen
    An implementation of the model object 'Gen'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Pos Gen Z
    • Neg Gen Z
    • Zero Gen Z
    • ZMulti Factor
    • Grounding
